WEBVTT

00:00:00.741 --> 00:00:02.383
San.

00:00:02.383 --> 00:00:05.204
U njemu provedemo oko trećine života,

00:00:05.204 --> 00:00:08.525
ali da li iko razume
o čemu se tu zapravo radi?

00:00:08.525 --> 00:00:10.740
Galen, jedan od najznačajnijih lekara

00:00:10.740 --> 00:00:12.880
starog veka je pre 2.000 godina

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:13.939
pretpostavio da se

00:00:13.939 --> 00:00:16.258
pokretačka sila našeg mozga,

00:00:16.258 --> 00:00:19.620
njegovo gorivo, dok smo budni

00:00:19.620 --> 00:00:22.190
sliva u ostatak tela

00:00:22.190 --> 00:00:26.204
i oživljava ga, ali isušuje mozak,

00:00:26.204 --> 00:00:27.820
a dok spavamo,

00:00:27.820 --> 00:00:30.358
sva ta vlaga iz ostatka tela